        "text": "The document is a page from the California Independent System Operator Corporation's Fifth Replacement Electronic Tariff, specifically Appendix F to the LGIA (Large Generator Interconnection Agreement). It outlines sections for \"Addresses for Delivery of Notices and Billings,\" which are currently placeholders marked as \"[To be supplied.]\" for three entities: Participating TO (Transmission Owner), Interconnection Customer, and CAISO (California Independent System Operator). The document is dated September 1, 2022, and labeled as Appendix CC.",
