      {
        "id": "5e40035b-8b54-46fb-bd99-69e9194eae69",
        "score": 0.49444407,
        "text": "The document is a page from the \"California Independent System Operator Corporation Fifth Replacement Electronic Tariff.\" It is labeled as Appendix Z and dated September 1, 2022. The content for this section is not provided, as indicated by the placeholder \"[To be supplied.]\"",
