        "text": "The document is a cover page for Appendix DD of the California Independent System Operator Corporation's Fifth Replacement Tariff. It is titled \"Generator Interconnection and Deliverability Allocation Procedures (GIDAP)\" and is dated December 17, 2024. The page serves as an introduction to the appendix, which likely details procedures related to generator interconnection and deliverability allocation.",
