        "text": "The document is a page from the California Independent System Operator Corporation's Fifth Replacement Electronic Tariff. It is labeled as \"Schedule G\" and is marked \"Not Used.\" The date on the document is February 15, 2021, and it is identified as Appendix G. There is no additional content or information provided on this page.",
